{{see|bailey}}
==English==
To be a Bailey is to be a unsociable person. often a male and has no friends of the oposite sex. a grown person who acts a lot younger than they are. Often called a Moron or Jackass.

===Proper noun===
'''Bailey'''
# an [[English]] [[occupational name]] for a [[steward]] or [[official]]
# an English [[topographic]] [[surname]] from someone who lived by a [[bailey]] (the outer wall of a castle)

